{% extends "team/base.html.twig" %}

{% block title %}Print - {{ parent() }}{% endblock %}

{% block content %}

    <br>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="text-center">Notice 注意</h3>
                Due to technical reasons, please add a piece of comment at the beginning of your code to tell us your teamname and your detailed location (accurate to your seat number) if you wish to print your code. 
                If you fail to do so, we may not be able to deliver the printed code to you.
                Thank you for your understanding.<br>
                由于技术原因，如果您需要代码打印服务，请在代码开头添加一段注释告知我们您的队伍名称、比赛时所在校区、机房和座位信息。
                如果您没有添加上述信息，我们可能将无法把打印好的代码送达给您。
                感谢您的理解。<br>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="text-center">Print source 代码打印服务</h3>
                {{ form(form) }}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{% endblock %}

{% block extrafooter %}
    {% include 'partials/javascript_print.html.twig' %}
{% endblock %}
